### Get random screenshot

GET {{url}}/api/v1/screenshot/weighted?markViewed={{markViewed}}
Authorization: Creator {{creatorName}};{{creatorId}};{{hwid}}

> {%
    client.global.set("screenshot", response.body);
%}

### Get random screenshot weighted algorithms

GET {{url}}/api/v1/screenshot/weighted
    ?random=10
    &recent=10
    &archeologist=10
    &supporter=10
    &markViewed={{markViewed}}
    &viewMaxAge=1
Authorization: Creator {{creatorName}};{{creatorId}};{{hwid}}

> {%
    client.global.set("screenshot", response.body);
%}

### Report a screenshot

POST {{url}}/api/v1/screenshot/report
Authorization: Creator {{creatorName}};{{creatorId}};{{hwid}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "screenshotId": "{{screenshot.id}}"
}

### Upload a screenshot

POST {{url}}/api/v1/screenshot/upload
Authorization: Creator {{creatorName}};{{creatorId}};{{hwid}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="creatorName"

toverux

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="cityName"

Colossal City

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="cityMilestone"

20

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="cityPopulation"

1200

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="screenshot"; filename="screenshot.jpg"

< screenshot.jpg
--WebAppBoundary--
